<% content_for :accessibility do %>
  <p>We're constantly working to make our service as accessible and usable as possible.</p>
  <h2>Compatibility with tools</h2>
  <p>The service is compatible with recent versions of the following screen readers:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Jaws</li>
    <li>Supernova Screen Readers</li>
    <li>Voiceover</li>
  </ul>
  <p>The site should also be compatible with:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>basic operating system screen magnifier</li>
    <li>operating system speech packages</li>
  </ul>
  <h2>Get help</h2>
  <p>You can find guidance from the BBC about:</p>
  <ul class="list-bullet">
    <li><%= link_to 'making your mouse easier to use', 'http://www.bbc.co.uk/accessibility/guides/mouse_easier/', class: 'external', rel: 'external' %></li>
    <li><%= link_to 'using your keyboard to control your mouse', 'http://www.bbc.co.uk/accessibility/guides/keyboard_mouse/', class: 'external', rel: 'external' %></li>
    <li><%= link_to 'alternatives to a keyboard and mouse', 'http://www.bbc.co.uk/accessibility/guides/alternative_devices/', class: 'external', rel: 'external' %></li>
    <li><%= link_to 'increasing the size of the text in your web browser', 'http://www.bbc.co.uk/accessibility/guides/text_larger/', class: 'external', rel: 'external' %></li>
    <li><%= link_to 'changing text and background colours', 'http://www.bbc.co.uk/accessibility/guides/change_colours/', class: 'external', rel: 'external' %></li>
    <li><%= link_to 'how to magnify your screen', 'http://www.bbc.co.uk/accessibility/guides/magnify/', class: 'external', rel: 'external' %></li>
    <li><%= link_to 'screen readers and talking browsers', 'http://www.bbc.co.uk/accessibility/guides/screenreaders/', class: 'external', rel: 'external' %></li>
  </ul>
  <h2>Leave feedback</h2>
  <p>You should contact_us. if you have trouble using our service - this will help us to make improvements </p>
<% end %>
